<span id="Part_tools_toolbar"></span>
=== Panel nástrojů Part ===

* [[Image:Sketcher_NewSketch.svg|32px]] [[Sketcher_NewSketch/cs|Nový náčrt]]: Vytvoří nový náčrt a otevře dialogové okno [[Sketcher_Dialog/cs|Sketcheru]] pro jeho úpravy.

* [[Image:Part_Extrude.svg|32px]] [[Part_Extrude/cs|Vysunutí]]: Extruduje rovinné plochy.

* [[Image:Part_Revolve.svg|32px]] [[Part_Revolve/cs|Orotování]]: Vytvoří těleso otáčením objektu (který není tělesem) kolem osy.

* [[Image:Part_Mirror.svg|32px]] [[Part_Mirror/cs|Zrcadlit]]: Zrcadlí vybraný objekt přes zrcadlovou rovinu.

* [[Image:Part_Scale.svg|32px]] [[Part_Scale/cs|Změna velikosti]]: Změní rozměry jednoho nebo více tvarů. {{Version|1.0}}

* [[Image:Part_Fillet.svg|32px]] [[Part_Fillet/cs|Zaoblení]]: Zaoblí hrany objektu.

* [[Image:Part_Chamfer.svg|32px]] [[Part_Chamfer/cs|Zkosení]]: Zkosí hrany objektu.

* [[File:Part_MakeFace.svg|32px]] [[Part_MakeFace/cs|Plocha z drátů]]: Vytvoří plochu ze sady drátů (obrysů).

* [[Image:Part_RuledSurface.svg|32px]] [[Part_RuledSurface/cs|Zakřivená plocha]]: Vytvoří zakřivenou plochu.

* [[Image:Part_Loft.svg|32px]] [[Part_Loft/cs|Profilování]]: Přechody mezi jednotlivými profily.

* [[Image:Part_Sweep.svg|32px]] [[Part_Sweep/cs|Tažení]]: Provede vytažení jednoho nebo více profilů podél dráhy.

* [[Image:Part_Section.svg|32px]] [[Part_Section/cs|Řez]]: Vytvoří řez průnikem objektu s rovinou řezu.

* [[Image:Part_CrossSections.svg|32px]] [[Part_CrossSections/cs|Řezy]]: Vytvoří jeden nebo více řezů objektem.

* <span id="Part_CompOffsetTools">[[Image:Part_Offset.svg|x32px]][[Image:Toolbar_flyout_arrow_blue_background.svg|x32px]] Odsazení:</span><!--Do not edit span id: the Part_CompOffsetTools pages redirect here-->

:* [[Image:Part_Offset.svg|32px]] [[Part_Offset/cs|3D odsazení]]: Vytvoří rovnoběžný obrazec v určité vzdálenosti od originálu.

:* [[Image:Part_Offset2D.svg|32px]] [[Part_Offset2D/cs|2D Odsazení]]: Vytvoří rovnoběžnou přímku v určité vzdálenosti od původní přímky nebo zvětší/zmenší rovinnou plochu.

* [[Image:Part_Thickness.svg|32px]] [[Part_Thickness/cs|Tloušťka]]: Vydlabe dutinu v plném tělesu.

<div class="mw-translate-fuzzy">
* [[File:Part_ProjectionOnSurface.svg|32px]] [[Part_ProjectionOnSurface/cs|Průmět na povrch: Promítá logo, text nebo libovolný tvar, drát či hranu na povrch.
</div>

<div class="mw-translate-fuzzy">
* [[File:Part_ColorPerFace.svg|32px]] [[Part_ColorPerFace/cs|Vzhled jednotlivých ploch: Přiřazuje barvy jednotlivým plochám objektů.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
=== Boolean toolbar ===
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* <span id="Part_CompCompoundTools">[[Image:Part_Compound.svg|x32px]][[Image:Toolbar_flyout_arrow_blue_background.svg|x32px]] Compound:</span><!--Do not edit span id: the Part_CompCompoundTools pages redirect here-->
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
:* [[Image:Part_Compound.svg|32px]] [[Part_Compound|Compound]]: Creates a compound from the selected objects.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
:* [[Image:Part_ExplodeCompound.svg|32px]] [[Part_ExplodeCompound|Explode Compound]]: Splits up compounds.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
:* [[Image:Part_CompoundFilter.svg|32px]] [[Part_CompoundFilter|Compound Filter]]: Extracts the individual pieces from compounds.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* [[Image:Part_Boolean.svg|32px]] [[Part_Boolean|Boolean Operation]]: Performs boolean operations on two objects.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* [[Image:Part_Cut.svg|32px]] [[Part_Cut|Cut]]: Cuts one object from another.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* [[Image:Part_Fuse.svg|32px]] [[Part_Fuse|Union]]: Fuses two or more objects.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* [[Image:Part_Common.svg|32px]] [[Part_Common|Intersection]]: Extracts the common part of two objects.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* <span id="Part_CompJoinFeatures">[[Image:Part_JoinConnect.svg|x32px]][[Image:Toolbar_flyout_arrow_blue_background.svg|x32px]] Join:</span><!--Do not edit span id: the Part_CompJoinFeatures pages redirect here-->
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
:* [[Image:Part_JoinConnect.svg|32px]] [[Part_JoinConnect|Connect Shapes]]: Connects interiors of walled objects.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
:* [[Image:Part_JoinEmbed.svg|32px]] [[Part_JoinEmbed|Embed Shapes]]: Embeds a walled object into another walled object.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
:* [[Image:Part_JoinCutout.svg|32px]] [[Part_JoinCutout|Cutout Shape]]: Creates a cutout in a wall of an object for another walled object.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* <span id="Part_CompSplittingTools">[[Image:Part_BooleanFragments.svg|x32px]][[Image:Toolbar_flyout_arrow_blue_background.svg|x32px]] Split:</span><!--Do not edit span id: the Part_CompSplittingTools pages redirect here-->
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
:* [[Image:Part_BooleanFragments.svg|32px]] [[Part_BooleanFragments|Boolean Fragments]]: Creates all pieces obtained from Boolean operations.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
:* [[Image:Part SliceApart.svg|32px]] [[Part_SliceApart|Slice Apart]]: Slices and splits an object by intersecting it with other objects.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
:* [[Image:Part_Slice.svg|32px]] [[Part_Slice|Slice to Compound]]: Slices an object by intersecting it with other objects.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
:* [[Image:Part_XOR.svg|32px]] [[Part_XOR|Boolean XOR]]: Removes space shared by an even number of objects.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* [[File:Part_CheckGeometry.svg|32px]] [[Part_CheckGeometry|Check Geometry]]: Checks the geometry of selected objects for errors.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* [[Image:Part Defeaturing.svg|32px]] [[Part_Defeaturing|Defeaturing]]: Removes features from an object.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
=== Other tools ===
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* [[File:Part_BoxSelection.svg|32px]] [[Part_BoxSelection|Box Selection]]: Selects faces from a rectangular area.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* [[File:Part_ShapeFromMesh.svg|32px]] [[Part_ShapeFromMesh|Shape From Mesh]]: Creates shapes from mesh objects.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* [[File:Part_PointsFromMesh.svg|32px]] [[Part_PointsFromMesh|Points From Shape]]: Creates points objects from geometric objects.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* [[File:Part_MakeSolid.svg|32px]] [[Part_MakeSolid|Convert to Solid]]: Creates solids from shape objects.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* [[File:Part_ReverseShape.svg|32px]] [[Part_ReverseShape|Reverse Shapes]]: Creates parametric copies with reversed face normals from selected objects.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* Copy:
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
:* [[File:Part_SimpleCopy.svg|32px]] [[Part_SimpleCopy|Simple Copy]]: Creates non-parametric copies of objects.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
:* [[File:Part_TransformedCopy.svg|32px]] [[Part_TransformedCopy|Transformed Copy]]: Creates non-parametric copies of objects. It is intended for objects nested in containers.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
:* [[File:Part_ElementCopy.svg|32px]] [[Part_ElementCopy|Shape Element Copy]]: Creates non-parametric copies of subelements: vertices, edges and faces.
</div> 

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
:* [[Image:Part_RefineShape.svg|32px]] [[Part_RefineShape|Refine Shape]]: Creates parametric copies with a refined shape from selected objects. It removes unnecessary edges from planar and cylindrical faces.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* [[Image:Part_ToleranceSet.svg|32px]] [[Part_ToleranceSet|Set Tolerance]]: creates a parametric copy of selected objects with all contained tolerances set to at least a certain minimum value. {{Version|1.1}}
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* [[Image:Part_SectionCut.svg|32px]] [[Part_SectionCut|Persistent Section Cut]]: Creates persistent cuts of objects and assemblies.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* [[Image:Part_EditAttachment.svg|32px]] [[Part_EditAttachment|Attachment]]: Attaches an object to one or more other objects.
</div>

