<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* [[Image:Part_Measure_Toggle_3D.svg|32px]] [[Part_Measure_Toggle_3D|Toggle 3D]]: Shows or hides 3D measurements. Not available in {{VersionPlus|1.0}}.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
